[Player 1 Katamari Ball Size Modifier]
author=bungholio
description=Don&#039;t increase too much at a time or the game will stop.  You can get
to any big size on any level, just don&#039;t do a sudden jump from 10cm to
50m.  Use jokers to set them.  You will be able to roll up anything very
fast.  It uses floats, but they seem unpredictable.  I have a big list.
36000000 - 1cm 5mm
37000000 - 2cm 4mm
38000000 - 3cm 9mm
39000000 - 6cm 1mm
3a000000 - 9cm 7mm
3b000000 - 15cm 5mm
3c000000 - 24cm 6mm
3d000000 - 39cm
3e000000 - 62cm
3f000000 - 98cm 4mm
3f800000 - 1m 24cm
40000000 - 1m 56cm 3mm
40400000 - 1m 78cm 9mm
40800000 - 1m 96cm 9mm
41000000 - 2m 48cm 1mm
41800000 - 3m 12cm 6mm
42000000 - 3m 93cm 9mm
42800000 - 4m 96cm 3mm
43000000 - 6m 25cm 2mm
43800000 - 7m 87cm 8mm
44000000 - 9m 92cm 5mm
44800000 - 12m 50cm 5mm
45000000 - 15m 75cm 6mm
45800000 - 19m 85cm 1mm
46000000 - 25m 01cm 1mm
46800000 - 31m 51cm 1mm
47000000 - 39m 70cm 2mm
47800000 - 50m 02cm 2mm
48000000 - 63m 02cm 3mm
48800000 - 79m 40cm 4mm
49000000 - 100m 04cm 3mm
49800000 - 126m 04cm 7mm
4a000000 - 158m 80cm 9mm
4a800000 - 200m 08cm 7mm
4b000000 - 252m 09cm 4mm
4b800000 - 317m 61cm 8mm
4c000000 - 400m 17cm 4mm
4c800000 - 504m 18cm 7mm
4d000000 - 635m 23cm 6mm
4d800000 - 800m 34cm 7mm
patch=1,EE,209889BC,extended,36000000

[Player 1 Size Modifier]
author=bungholio
description=L2 + Up = Increase Size, L2 + Down = Decrease Size
patch=1,EE,D101BE82,extended,0000FEEF
patch=1,EE,30200004,extended,009889BE
patch=1,EE,D101BE82,extended,0000FEBF
patch=1,EE,30300004,extended,009889BE

[Player 1 Speed Modifier]
author=bungholio
description=It&#039;s floats.  Just give it something like 3f000000, 40000000, 41000000,
and just keep increasing it like that or maybe more at a time.  It
determines how far away the prince is from the katamari ball, which can
make you very fast.  The game usually adjusts this for you as you grow.
As you grow you will start slowing down so keep setting it with the jokers
if you want.  I could barely move if I set it too fast too soon.
patch=1,EE,209889C8,extended,00000000

[Player 1 Speed Modifier]
author=bungholio
description=L2 + Right = Increase Speed, L2 + Left = Decrease Speed
patch=1,EE,D101BE82,extended,0000FEDF
patch=1,EE,30200004,extended,009889CA
patch=1,EE,D101BE82,extended,0000FE7F
patch=1,EE,30300004,extended,009889CA

