[Time Modifier]
author=bungholio
description=The game counts by 1/10ths of a second.  1 second is &quot;A&quot; hex, so
multiply seconds by A.  I know 3 minutes is 708 hex.  708 hex = 1800
decimal.  3 minutes is 180 seconds.  1800 / 180 = 10 = &quot;A&quot; hex.
patch=1,EE,2054EAA8,extended,00000000

